Annuity_TaxQualification.RulesforWizard: 1. Default = Blank;2. If Owner_Type = Individual then include list options = Blank,Non-Qualified,Traditional IRA,Roth IRA,SEP IRA;3. If Owner_Type = Joint,Trust,Corporation then include list options = Blank,Non-Qualified;4. If Owner_Type = Custodian then include list options = Blank,Traditional IRA,Roth IRA,SEP IRA

Owner_FirstName.RulesforWizard: Default = Blank;If Owner_Type = Individual,Joint then display and enable else Owner_Type = Trust,Custodian,Corporation then disable and hide
Owner_FirstName.ValidationRules: If Owner_FirstName = blank then Issue Error Message: Owner First Name is required.

Annuitant_SameAsOwner.RulesforWizard: Default = Unselected;If Owner_Type = Individual,Joint then display and enable else Owner_Type = Trust,Custodian,Corporation then set to No and disable

Owner_TIN.RulesforWizard: Default = Blank;If Owner_Type = Trust,Custodian,Corporation then display and enable else Owner_Type = Individual,Joint then hide and disable
Owner_TIN.ValidationRules: If Owner_TIN = blank then Issue Error Message: Owner TIN is required.;If Owner_TIN = Invalid then Issue Error Message: Please enter a valid TIN for Owner.
